<item>
            <title>[LU-1418] (osc_lock.c:1099:osc_lock_enqueue_wait()) DEADLOCK POSSIBLE! - too many </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1418</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The console log contains 100&apos;s of &quot;DEADLOCK POSSIBLE!&quot; errors, followed by debug data and a stack trace. The messages sound like something is seriously wrong, but there&apos;s no sign that a deadlock has actually occurred. To the contrary, evidence indicates that the app continues executing and completes successfully.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="14469">LU-1418</key>
            <summary>(osc_lock.c:1099:osc_lock_enqueue_wait()) DEADLOCK POSSIBLE! - too many </summary>
